messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com
Hello! Welcome to FightLust.com! How can we support you in your journey towards healing today?
I'm here to assist you, but I'm not a real person—I'm a customer support assistant. If you need to speak with a human agent, I can help with that! Would you like me to connect you?

We understand that sometimes you need to talk to a real person for prayer, guidance, or encouragement. We are here to support you. Please hold as we connect you with a ministry team member who can assist you in your journey. If you’re unable to reach someone, feel free to email us at prayer@fightlust.com.
